Geoffrey Kerr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geoffrey_Kerr 0 Geoffrey Kerr (26 January 1895 – 1 July 1971) was a British stage and film actor and writer, during the middle of the 20th century, part of a British family with a strong stage and theatre tradition spanning several generations.
